The QR code decoding implementation in liblierre (src/decode/, src/internal/decoder.h)
is derived from quirc. The original data structures, algorithms, and perspective
transform functions were adapted with modifications including type changes, renamed
identifiers, and integration with libpoporon for Reed-Solomon error correction.

